Model averaged predictions for CCME Boron Data

Source: R/data.R
boron_pred.Rd

A data frame of the predictions based on 1,000 bootstrap iterations.

boron_pred

Format

A tbl data frame:

percent

The percent of species affected <int>.

est

The estimated concentration <dbl>.

se

The standard error of the estimate <dbl>.

lcl

The lower confidence limit <dbl>.

se

The upper confidence limit <dbl>.

Examples

head(boron_pred)
#> # A tibble: 6 x 5
#>   percent   est    se   lcl   ucl
#>     <int> <dbl> <dbl> <dbl> <dbl>
#> 1       1 0.304 0.342 0.125  1.08
#> 2       2 0.544 0.467 0.236  1.68
#> 3       3 0.780 0.568 0.353  2.23
#> 4       4 1.01  0.658 0.476  2.75
#> 5       5 1.25  0.741 0.603  3.25
#> 6       6 1.49  0.819 0.736  3.73
